With all 404 precincts reporting, Murphy led Wagner in the vote tally with 49,530 votes to 19,338. Three other candidates, Gary Henderson, Chaston Roston Jr. and Robert Pirchesky had 2.5, 1.4 and 1.3 percent of the votes, respectively.")
